PG| ***** 76 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I will preempt with and any hands with less than 10 HCP, meaning I must have a long suit somewhere. It is reasonable for partner to assume I have some defense when I open at the 1-level (although sometimes I might not). The fewer HCP I have, the more the opps have, so preempting is more effective. Therefore,:|
