NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|When you play ^*BDelayed DONT^*N, it applies over a 1N overcall, or if it goes, for example, 1S-P-1N-?. It basically works the same as DONT, with a couple of small exceptions.|
